Subprocessors
Effective date: February 13, 2026

This page lists third-party subprocessors Polsia may use to deliver the service. Actual usage depends on enabled product features, account settings, and environment configuration.

Vendor	Primary purpose	Typical data categories
Stripe	Payments, subscriptions, billing portal, checkout	Billing identifiers, transaction metadata, subscription status
Postmark	Transactional and operational email delivery/inbound processing	Email addresses, message content, delivery metadata
Meta (Pixel/CAPI)	Marketing attribution and ad conversion measurement	Hashed identifiers, event metadata, _fbp/_fbc, IP/UA
Google (OAuth/Gmail APIs)	Authentication and optional connected account functionality	OAuth profile fields, authorized account metadata, tokens
GitHub	Optional repository integration and automation tasks	OAuth tokens, repo metadata, action logs
Slack	Optional workspace integrations and notifications	OAuth tokens, channel metadata, message metadata
Sentry	Error monitoring and diagnostics	Application errors, stack traces, technical telemetry
Render	Application and infrastructure hosting	Service/runtime metadata, operational logs
Neon (PostgreSQL)	Managed database hosting	Application-stored customer/account and product data
Redis provider	Queueing, pub/sub, short-term operational state	Transient job and session-related operational metadata
Cloudflare R2	Object storage for uploaded/generated assets	Files, media assets, related metadata
Anthropic / AWS Bedrock / OpenAI	LLM and AI model execution (as configured)	Prompts, tool context, generated outputs, model telemetry
Late.dev	Social account posting/integration workflows	Social account IDs, post metadata, OAuth credentials
Hunter.io	Email verification and lookup (optional features)	Email addresses and verification metadata
IPinfo	IP geolocation (optional enrichment)	IP address, coarse location metadata
Fal.ai	AI media generation features	Generation prompts and generated media metadata
ScreenshotOne	Automated screenshot generation	Requested URLs/pages and generated image metadata
Updates to This List
We may update this list as vendors or service architecture changes. Material updates are reflected by updating the effective date on this page.

Related Notices
See our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service for details about how personal data is handled.

